        <abstract>
            <p>Discusses the worsening relations between their two countries and the possibility of war.</p> 
<p>Expects <hi rend="italic">Orchids</hi> and his <hi rend="italic">Primula</hi> paper [<hi rend="italic">Collected papers</hi> 2: 45–63] to be out soon.</p> 
            <p>Thanks AG for some facts on dimorphism.</p> 
<p>George Bentham has given him a list of <hi rend="italic">Oxalis</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Mentha</hi> species that are dimorphic like <hi rend="italic">Primula</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Is in a "thick mud" regarding design in nature.</p>
        </abstract>
